.SH NAME
shelly-group-list - List all device groups


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly group list [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
List all device groups and their member counts.

.PP
Groups allow organizing devices for batch operations. Each group can
contain multiple devices, and devices can belong to multiple groups.

.PP
Output is formatted as a table by default. Use -o json or -o yaml for
structured output suitable for scripting.

.PP
Columns: Name, Devices (count)


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for list


